      <script type="text/javascript">
       //inp_masterSearch


    function search_OnClick() {

        var inp = document.getElementById('inp_masterSearch');
        if (inp.value.trim() == "Search" || inp.value.trim() == "") {
            inp.value = "";
        }
    }

    function search_OnBlur() {
        // alert("blur");
        var inp = document.getElementById('inp_masterSearch');
        var inpTxt = inp.value.trim();

        if (inpTxt == "") {
            inp.value = " Search";
        }
    }




    function search_OnKeyDown(e) {

        var inp = document.getElementById('inp_masterSearch');
        var inpTxt = inp.value.trim();

        var sub = false;
        //FireFox
        if (e.which == 13 &amp;&amp; inpTxt != '') { //13=enter
            sub = true;
        }

        //all other browers
        if (event.keyCode == 13 &amp;&amp; inpTxt != '') {
            sub = true;
        }


        if (sub == true) {
            Search_Go();
            e.preventDefault();
        }

    }

    function Search_Go() {
        var inp = document.getElementById('inp_masterSearch');
        var inpTxt = inp.value.trim();


        var reg = new RegExp("[^a-zA-Z0-9,\s]", "g");
        var searchTerm = inpTxt.replace(reg, "");

        window.location.href = "/Search.aspx?sp=" + searchTerm;

    }
      </script>

       <script type="text/javascript">
        function ShowMenu(selected_id, subMenuID) {

        var bgColor = document.getElementById(selected_id).style.backgroundColor;
        var sameTd = 0;
        var hasSub = 0;


        if (bgColor == '' || bgColor == 'transparent') {
            sameTd = 0;
        }
        else {
            sameTd = 1;
        }


        try {
            //Get Code from SubMenu
            var SubMenu = document.getElementById(subMenuID).innerHTML;

            //Copy submenu code into show Container
            document.getElementById('div_SubMenu').innerHTML = SubMenu;
            // document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').innerHTML = SubMenu;
            hasSub = 1;
        }
        catch (e) {  //doesn't have a sub menu
            hasSub = 0;
            document.getElementById('div_SubMenu').innerHTML = "";
            //document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').innerHTML = "";
        }

        //reset color
        var MenuTDs = document.getElementById('div_menu').getElementsByTagName('td');
        for (var i = 0; i &lt; MenuTDs.length; i++) {
            MenuTDs[i].style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
            MenuTDs[i].style.color = 'black'; //#4f4f4f   757575
        }

        //set selected color
        document.getElementById(selected_id).style.backgroundColor = 'black'; // '#757575'; // '#C6C6C6';
        document.getElementById(selected_id).style.color = 'white'; //'#4F4F4F'; // 'transparent';

        // var jq_divSubMenu = "#div_SubMenu";
        var jq_divSubMenu = "#div_OuterSub";


        //set height
        //var MenuHeight = document.getElementById("div_SubMenu").scrollHeight + 'px';
        //document.getElementById("div_OpacBg").style.height = MenuHeight;
        //document.getElementById("div_OuterSub").style.height = MenuHeight;  


        if (sameTd == 1) {
            //A
            document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').style.display = 'none';   //$(jq_divSubMenu).slideUp("400");


            //B
            //reset color
            document.getElementById(selected_id).style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
            document.getElementById(selected_id).style.color = 'black';  //'#4F4F4F'   757575;
        }
        else if (sameTd == 0) {
            //C
            document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').style.display = 'none'; // $(jq_divSubMenu).hide();

            //D
            if (hasSub == 1) {
                //Set Div Heights

                //E
                document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').style.display = 'block'; // $(jq_divSubMenu).slideDown("slow");


                // $(jq_divSubMenu).hide().css('height', 'auto').slideDown();
                // $(jq_divSubMenu).slideToggle("slow");
                //F

            }
        }

        //        var effect = 'slide';
        //        var options = { direction: "up" };
        //        var duration = 500;
        //        $('#div_OuterSub').toggle(effect, options, duration);

        //G      alert('g' + document.getElementById("div_SubMenu").scrollHeight);

        //   Set Div Heights
        var MenuHeight = document.getElementById("div_SubMenu").scrollHeight + 'px';
        document.getElementById("div_OpacBg").style.height = MenuHeight;
        document.getElementById("div_OuterSub").style.height = MenuHeight;



    }


    function ShowSubMenu(subMenuID, RootID) {

        var hdrID = 'tdRMM_' + RootID;

        var hasSub = 0;


        try {
            //Get Code from SubMenu
            var SubMenu = document.getElementById(subMenuID).innerHTML;

            //Copy submenu code into show Container
            document.getElementById('div_SubMenu').innerHTML = SubMenu;
            //document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').innerHTML = SubMenu;
            hasSub = 1;
        }
        catch (e) {  //doesn't have a sub menu
            hasSub = 0;
            document.getElementById('div_SubMenu').innerHTML = "";
            // document.getElementById('div_OuterSub').innerHTML = "";
        }


        // var jq_divSubMenu = "#div_SubMenu";
        var jq_divSubMenu = "#div_OuterSub";


        if (hasSub == 1) {
            $(jq_divSubMenu).slideDown("slow");
        }
        else {
            $(jq_divSubMenu).hide();
            //reset color
            document.getElementById(hdrID).style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
            document.getElementById(hdrID).style.color = 'black'; //'#4F4F4F'; 757575
        }

    }
       </script>
